{"tid":1391130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非策略討論］一於同佢玩機制玩到底！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:37:32.000Z","uid":241594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"111780e8f500f8ad07da3f5d6a370b20c74bd8b2","tid":1391130,"uid":241594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲因為種種原因，未必會親身上前線，但又好想參與好想今次運動成功，各位和理非一齊入黎傾下有咩可以做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我既睇法係，一定要同政府<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩機制</span></span></strong>玩到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回帶一下，我地既五大訴求係：<br />\n1. 徹底撤回修例<br />\n2. 收回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放義士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會 徹底返究黑警濫權<br />\n5. 全面實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求入面，<br />\n1,2 係要撬開林鄭或佢繼任人把口，要政府認錯向民意交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3 係要保護義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4, 5 係要政府處理現有管治問題，包括黑警管理問題同政制問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3係好重要，兄弟爬山唔止要各自努力，仲要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">齊上齊落</span></span></strong><br />\n當然繼續爭取政府特赦係上策，不過港共政權無恥，我認為要保護義士一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">籌錢幫佢地請最好既大狀打官司</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前暗角七警咁都有兩件打得甩，就係因為黑警有基金幫佢地籌錢請大狀<br />\n<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會係對訴求4,5有幫助，唯有成立獨立調查委員會，先至可以有獨立意見確認黑警管理有問題，民主受壓制，從而大條道理迫政府正視問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家連好多建制派都轉呔贊成成立獨立調查委員會，大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要力爭到底</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共已經好明確表示，只要唔搞港獨，唔暴力，大家可以隨便同林鄭算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢兩日港共就升級左拉人同告人，拉更多人，告更重罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果大家唔犯法，佢可以拉乜鳩告乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔犯法而要繼續俾壓力港共，唯一出路就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">頻密而大規模合法抗爭，罷工＋各區日日超多人遊行</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就煩到佢死，而佢又唔可以出黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}